Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two enemies left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three of us...\NIt's three against two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to do it with\None more contact if we do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right!\NLet's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's four against two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting Akamaru,\Nit's four against two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish it quickly with\Nour new technique next!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, say. If necessary,\NI'll do an awesome Shadow Clone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so it'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's reassuring...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But my strategy comes first. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For that purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to catch up\Nbefore the sun sets at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's starting to set...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Jirobo nor\NKidomaru have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they're having\Na hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter...\NMore important is Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only completed one-third\Nof the journey in half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have Curse Marks, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions asked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be different\Nthan that time before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with your surprise attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much interference...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know whether\Nwe'll make it in time at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We still can't catch up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll maintain this distance\Nand continue the pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're delaying\Nthe attack until dawn breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real!\NWe can't afford such leisure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Besides, if we're going\Nto attack anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it more advantageous\Nto use the darkness and attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, the darkness works\Nto our advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,only the moment\Nwe launch the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be close to impossible\Nto grab Sasuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,get away from them and escape\Nto a safe location
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in just that one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we couldn't get Sasuke\Nback in that one moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd probably just focus\Non guarding the coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, we wouldn't stand\Na chance in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for the part where they wouldn't\Nhave to move needlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly they'd get the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a different story\Nif we had Neji's Byakugan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you forgetting Akamaru's nose\Nand mine as well??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure to include your senses\Nof smell in the calculations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, up ahead they have\Nthe geographical advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can't use my Jutsu,\Nit'll be no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I seal off their movements\Nwith Shadow Possession Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect would be reduced to half\Nif clouds were to cover the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a drag, but there are too many\Ndangers, and uncertain elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow your instructions, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:06.42,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,556)}Recapture The Vessel \N Did Not Make It in Time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Recapture The Vessel \N Did Not Make It in Time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tayuya!\NWill we really make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just told to deliver\NMaster Sasuke by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that we have\Nlots of time to spare,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess we'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No Sasuke... yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running out of time...\NHe can't go on any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Several bodies have been\Nprepared for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And... you could even use me,\Nif necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you think I 've waited?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of urgency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage's Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His curse was stronger\Nthan expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! Sealing Jutsu!\NReaper Death Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't "reanimate" right now,\Nyou'll lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've selected and prepared\Nproficient bodies for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me! Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the recovery\Nof Sasuke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I use Kimimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall release you from this prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it'll only\Nbe one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all that's left is to\Nwake up Kimimaro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't summoned this time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kabuto, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your role is now finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Sound Ninja Five now,\NKimimaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... still haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your replacement has\Nalready been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses power equal\Nto your "Earth" Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been given\Nthe "Heaven" Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, he even\Nhas a Kekkei Genkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder who's stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NDon't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kabuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My life, how much do I have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,P-People... People are born\Nwith some kind of meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since people are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be some kind\Nof important calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I've started thinking so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That the meaning for being born...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For people, finding the meaning is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the only freedom God has given.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Lord Orochimaru\Nis now suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unprecedented\Ndifficult situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll mince no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've now lost your value\Nas a "vessel."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A new vessel is heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point in time,\Nit's too late, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! You said you were going\Nto let one person out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to keep\Nyour promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?\NOpen the door now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There was another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I...\NI'll be eaten here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shall grant you\Njust one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My clan that was captured\Nfor your experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Consider it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your strong will is going to remain\Nas Residual Aura inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you'll lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, your flesh is mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Lord Orochimaru's body\Nwill, once again
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,be unable to reanimate\Nfor several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is the next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-lndeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,my body no longer has value\Nas a vessel for Reanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It will now be difficult for me\Nwho has lost everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to find my own calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally understood that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring in the new "vessel"\Neven if it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my repayment to\NLord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only redemption\Nfor me for being worthless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we almost there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It should still take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What were those idiots\NJirobo and Kidomaru doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll take care of\Nthis nice and quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple Fists Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakra in his palm...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone Transformation, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way... His hands now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point if\NI catch you before you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,T unneling Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This was also a Shadow Clone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Luring Sakon into alignment with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and aiming at me from the start?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you succeeded\Njust with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been nailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Possession Jutsu succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A diversion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tayuya! What're you doing\Nidling away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you move forward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Kiba, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Punks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You scums... Messing around with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They were full of openings\Njust as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Having too much ability individually\Nis also a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it went just as calculated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in terms of teamwork,\Nours was way better than theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Comment: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:05.59,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.89,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.98,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.52,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.32,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:27.96,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:33.37,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:39.30,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:44.97,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:51.09,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:58.16,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:01.36,ED8,,0,0,0,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.33,ED8,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.80,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.84,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.57,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:13.64,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.15,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:19.35,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.89,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:24.86,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:29.49,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
